rows.label: qst002901_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, a word with you, mo!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0002
rows.name:
On a request from the Superbian
army, the Shibutsu-bu triplets of
Larus & Co. have come along, mo!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0003
rows.name:
But on second thought, there are
no customers here but you, mo!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0005
rows.name:
However, I can see that you are
carrying something important, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0006
rows.name:
So, if you'll take on a
request for a cheap price,
I'll forgive you, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0007
rows.name:
I want you to get something from these
Cliffs of Morytha that looks like it
could be sold as a product, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0008
rows.name:
If we sell it in other countries,
it'll be rare and we'll make
lots and lots of money, mo!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0009
rows.name: Our losses here will be covered, mo!

rows.label: qst002901_msg0011
rows.name:
This is Shibushibu's first time
here too, mo. So just gather
anything that looks valuable, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0101
rows.name:
I want you to bring me anything
of high rarity from here at
the Cliffs of Morytha, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0103
rows.name:
Still not enough, mo. I'm
counting on you, mo.

rows.label: qst002901_msg0104
rows.name: Mo mo! That's a lot, mo!
